Cleaned_df <- read_csv("Trademarks_only.csv") %>% 
  filter(str_detect(statement_text,"\"*\"")) %>% 
  mutate(wordmark = str_extract(statement_text, "\"(.*?)\""),
         clean_wordmark = str_remove_all(wordmark, "\"|\\.|,"))
